{
  "stem": "1222.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we became friends up till today, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Special, I'll tell you one incident there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was two little girls by the grave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I saw it with my own eyes, slowly digging out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They looked so cute in their beautiful clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they announced it in Ukrainian, whoever wants the clothes, they have to throw in the two [NON-ENGLISH], the two little girls, in the grave alive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "One son-of-a-gun woman came up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She took out the clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "She took them by the feet and threw them in-- in that thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "You could imagine my heart saw it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My eyes saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "My heart heard the screaming of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That's why I know things-- God, I'm-- I don't think so mentally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But many nights [SOBBING] I hear the screams of these people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I can't get it over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It's already 45, 50 years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "These screams are there, and I'll never-- I'll die with those screams probably.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I can't help it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They are there, my ears.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Doesn't matter what I do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I'm well off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It doesn't help me anything, but they're there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I can't get rid of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was close, because I knew the area, and I knew, more or less, because my father used to work for a lot of these farmers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew more or less some of them, they would be the killers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For the example, we had one man that I was there myself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I put in a head stone over him and over his nephew, a Baptist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have his pictures all over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He helped me and my friend so much that probably I wouldn't be alive if it's not for him and with food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I froze my feet.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
